  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of study is to investigate the effects of PSE Music with a &quot;home-based&quot; loaded
      STS exercise program on the functional strength, gross motor function, daily participation,
      exercise involvement, motor control, and gait speed for children with spastic diplegia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
